{"type": "article", "id": 24750, "title": "Lululemon 推出休闲服，以及，前耐克设计师正式在阿迪上岗｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。\r\n", "date": "2016-03-31T10:21:51Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 1936, "name": "香水"}, {"id": 17712, "name": "设计总监"}, {"id": 2528, "name": "离职"}, {"id": 25632, "name": "新任"}, {"id": 25633, "name": "休闲服"}, {"id": 7764, "name": "军绿"}, {"id": 12011, "name": "摇滚"}, {"id": 27, "name": "Nike"}, {"id": 8367, "name": "lululemon"}, {"id": 25634, "name": "Leonard"}, {"id": 686, "name": "adidas"}, {"id": 15558, "name": "Vince"}, {"id": 681, "name": "Ralph Lauren"}, {"id": 15344, "name": "Mango"}, {"id": 4485, "name": "J. Crew"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 48, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160608130121boPaK17gGfTuUQlt.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h2>一些重要的新闻：</h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/markets-news/ready-to-wear-sportswear/vince-holding-q4-beat-fashion-rea-laccone-christopher-la-police-10399765/\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><b>Vince 四季度胜预期</b></a>｜Vince 最近发布四季度财报结果，胜于华尔街对其的预估，截至 1 月 30 日的三个月内，净销售额从 9470 万美元下降了 13.6% 至 8180 万美元，可比同店销售额包括电商渠道在内上涨了 10.7%。<br></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/3/marc-dolce-nike-adidas-vice-president-creative-director\"><b>前 Nike 设计师成 Adidas 创意总监</b></a>｜Nike 前设计师 Marc Dolce  自 2014 年秋季从 Nike 离职后，今日正式宣布成为 Adidas 副总裁和创意总监，同时宣布 Adidas 将新增布鲁克林创造者工厂，新的空间将成为 Adidas 第一个全方位服务、点对点的设计空间。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://us.fashionmag.com/news/Lululemon-profit-beats-expectations-on-strong-holiday-sales,675351.html#.VvvuNoQrJQY\"><b> Lululemon 季度收益胜预期</b></a>｜加拿大运动服饰品牌 Lululemon 最近财报显示，品牌截至 1 月 31 日的季度利润超出预期，有赖于假日时段强劲的销售表现。净收入上涨了 17％ 至 7.043 亿美元，净收益则从去年同期的 1.109 亿美元上涨了 6% 至 1.174 亿美元。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://sg.fashionmag.com/news/Christine-Phung-to-serve-as-Creative-Director-at-Leonard-Paris,675581.html#.VvxnNYQrJQY\"><b>Leonard Paris 任命新创意总监</b></a>｜法国时装品牌 Leonard 继去年年底创意总监华裔设计师殷亦晴离任后，职位一直空缺，近日集团宣布将由 Christine Phung 担任新创意总监， 毕业于巴黎杜普蕾应用艺术学院(Duperré School of Applied Arts)和法国时尚学院（IFM），曾为 Christophe Lemaire、 Chloé、Vanessa Bruno 和 Dior 童装，以及 Lacoste 运动线工作。2011 年曾创立自己的品牌。</p>\n<h2>一些值得一看的：</h2>\n<p class=\"\">Nike Air Huarache Ultra 女鞋推出淡紫配色款：<br></p>\n<p class=\"multiple\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608130106DWSob4FXj7Cg9mHc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608130107dSvaBLQupxPK9ygN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608130107xPmKeM06Ypf9NFUO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608130107IBJub3oW1KPl5jaz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.whowhatwear.com/lululemon-lab-spring-2016\">Lululemon 近日推出了更适合日常的限量休闲款式</a>，黑白灰为主：<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608130108jOMcKWnUdYx26wq8.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7537037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608130108B5vp40j9iLhm6kVD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7537037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608130109f4ZymKi7Fhxae0zN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7537037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p>Karlie Kloss 又为<a href=\"http://www.fashiongonerogue.com/karlie-kloss-mango-april-2016-campaign/\"> Mango 拍摄了四月特辑</a>，展现不羁的 90 年代摇滚风尚：</p>\n<p class=\"multiple\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608130109B9LdG0qjV2ICgauN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67037037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608130110YQKzTlE94V3Z5aPh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70740741\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608130110TJV0gmWdkbh7SF6P.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75092593\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.fashiongonerogue.com/j-crew-minimal-style-spring-2016-shop/\">J. Crew 2016 的春季系列</a>看起来很低调简约：<br></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016060813011105ywdMq746JCmitQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.57592593\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608130111SJ21fV9h8tpC5dxg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.57592593\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"multiple\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608130111vjAhWZgS58D16KsX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608130112kt7JlbNPfviSWhR9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608130112DpCdmv8qZ5S31MhH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608130113CvEYRV0BS62hOxgd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\">hummel 旗下更街头风的副牌 hummel J，近日联手 monkey time 推出<a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/3/hummel-j-for-monkey-time-wastelands\">春夏款的“荒芜之地”胶囊系列</a>：<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608130113lOIEhg12sDRJWU78.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608130114CiSFOfIu426bRG1y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608130114hBIR43GdJcF0jyWE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608130115K7ckRpdfAEzahHbN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608130115zg3L5EvetCUrmSoD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">匈牙利模特 Barbara Palvin<a href=\"http://www.fashiongonerogue.com/barbara-palvin-armani-acqua-di-gioia-2016/\">  为阿玛尼 Acqua di Gioia 新香水拍</a>摄广告：<br></p>\n<p class=\"multiple\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608130115TwhecKvO19Ul7NEz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608130116m65L8gc0A2DzjTI4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608130116zPCmGn4i8YL1eDvA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\">去年宣布暂时离开模特界，转战演艺圈的 Cara Delevingne 近日成为 Saint Laurent 春季系列大片主角：<br></p>\n<p class=\"multiple\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608130117lQv9rs4Vq6TOW8bM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606081301181doAQeDViT0KbMg7.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608130118H4gOSAbl2R63zoED.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608130118MrZvIE9D0XhqY4O5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\">2012 年在台湾成立的 Ystudio 工作室，最近推出的黄铜系列文具看起来很经典，自动铅笔和圆珠笔的组合：<br></p>\n<p class=\"multiple\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606081301196G03cM4dUV857pY1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606081301195FXre3RK41tMdBci.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608130120EJFaRexyvgGkbcmT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/3/jordan-galaxy-white\">Jordan Brand 推出一款全白的皮质</a> Galaxy：<br></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608130120kcZ8d5nBtgshb9fE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"><br></p>\n\n\n"}